{"id":48,"parent_id":30,"book_id":95,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":48,"title":"2 Nephi 18","subtitle":"","short_title":"2 Ne.","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/18","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 18"],[".studySummary",["i","Christ will be as a stone of stumbling and a rock of offense—Seek the Lord, not peeping wizards—Turn to the law and to the testimony for guidance—Compare",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/8"},"Isaiah 8"],". About 559–545",["span.small","B.C."]]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/18.1","order":"05.13.018.5136"},["b","1"],"Moreover, the word of the Lord said unto me: Take thee a great",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"roll"],", and write in it with a man’s pen, concerning",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"Maher-shalal-hash-baz"],"."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/18.2","order":"05.13.018.5137"},["b","2"],"And I took unto me faithful",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"witnesses"],"to record, Uriah the priest, and Zechariah the son of Jeberechiah."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/18.3","order":"05.13.018.5138"},["b","3"],"And I went unto the prophetess; and she conceived and bare a son. Then said the Lord to me:",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"Call"],"his name, Maher-shalal-hash-baz."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/18.4","order":"05.13.018.5139"},["b","4"],"For behold,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"the child"],"shall",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"not"],"have knowledge to cry, My father, and my mother, before the riches of Damascus and the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_4c"},"spoil"],"of",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_4d"},"Samaria"],"shall be taken away before the king of",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_4e"},"Assyria"],"."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/18.5","order":"05.13.018.5140"},["b","5"],"The Lord spake also unto me again, saying:"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/18.6","order":"05.13.018.5141"},["b","6"],"Forasmuch as this people refuseth the waters of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"Shiloah"],"that go softly, and rejoice in",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"Rezin"],"and Remaliah’s son;"],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/18.7","order":"05.13.018.5142"},["b","7"],"Now therefore, behold, the Lord bringeth up upon them the waters of the river, strong and many, even the king of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"Assyria"],"and all his glory; and he shall come up over all his channels, and go over all his banks."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/18.8","order":"05.13.018.5143"},["b","8"],"And he shall pass through Judah; he shall overflow and go over, he shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"reach"],"even to the neck; and the stretching out of his wings shall fill the breadth of thy land, O Immanuel."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/18.9","order":"05.13.018.5144"},["b","9"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"Associate"],"yourselves, O ye people, and ye shall be broken in pieces; and give ear all ye of far countries; gird yourselves, and ye shall be broken in pieces; gird yourselves, and ye shall be broken in pieces."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/18.10","order":"05.13.018.5145"},["b","10"],"Take counsel together, and it shall come to naught; speak the word, and it shall not stand; for God is with us."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/18.11","order":"05.13.018.5146"},["b","11"],"For the Lord spake thus to me with a strong hand, and instructed me that I should not walk in the way of this people, saying:"],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/18.12","order":"05.13.018.5147"},["b","12"],"Say ye not, A confederacy, to all to whom this people shall say, A",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"confederacy"],"; neither fear ye their fear, nor be afraid."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/18.13","order":"05.13.018.5148"},["b","13"],"Sanctify the Lord of Hosts himself, and let him be your fear, and let him be your dread."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/18.14","order":"05.13.018.5149"},["b","14"],"And he shall be for a sanctuary; but for a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"stone"],"of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"stumbling"],", and for a",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_14c"},"rock"],"of",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_14d"},"offense"],"to both the houses of Israel, for a gin and a",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_14e"},"snare"],"to the inhabitants of Jerusalem."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/18.15","order":"05.13.018.5150"},["b","15"],"And many among them shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"stumble"],"and fall, and be broken, and be snared, and be taken."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/18.16","order":"05.13.018.5151"},["b","16"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"Bind"],"up the testimony, seal the law among my disciples."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/18.17","order":"05.13.018.5152"},["b","17"],"And I will wait upon the Lord, that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"hideth"],"his face from the house of Jacob, and I will look for him."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/18.18","order":"05.13.018.5153"},["b","18"],"Behold, I and the children whom the Lord hath given me are for",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"signs"],"and for wonders in Israel from the Lord of Hosts, which dwelleth in Mount Zion."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/18.19","order":"05.13.018.5154"},["b","19"],"And when they shall say unto you: Seek unto them that have",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"familiar spirits"],", and unto",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_19b"},"wizards"],"that peep and mutter—",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_19c"},"should not"],"a people seek unto their God for the living to hear from the dead?"],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/18.20","order":"05.13.018.5155"},["b","20"],"To the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"law"],"and to the testimony; and if they speak not according to this word, it is because there is no light in them."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/18.21","order":"05.13.018.5156"},["b","21"],"And they shall pass through it hardly bestead and hungry; and it shall come to pass that when they shall be hungry, they shall fret themselves, and curse their king and their God, and look upward."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/18.22","order":"05.13.018.5157"},["b","22"],"And they shall look unto the earth and behold trouble, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"darkness"],", dimness of anguish, and shall be driven to darkness."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/18.1a","order":"05.13.018.5158"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/8.1.1-22"},"Isa. 8:1 (1–22)"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/18.1b","order":"05.13.018.5160"},["b","1b"],["span.small","HEB"],"To speed to the spoil, he hasteneth the prey."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/18.2a","order":"05.13.018.5162"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/witness"},"TG Witness"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/18.3a","order":"05.13.018.5164"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/18.18"},"2 Ne. 18:18"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/18.4a","order":"05.13.018.5166"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/17.16"},"2 Ne. 17:16"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/18.4b","order":"05.13.018.5168"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/8.4"},"Isa. 8:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"4c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/18.4c","order":"05.13.018.5170"},["b","4c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/15.29.29-30"},"2 Kgs. 15:29 (29–30)"],"."],["div",{"id":"4d","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/18.4d","order":"05.13.018.5172"},["b","4d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/17.6"},"2 Kgs. 17:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"4e","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/18.4e","order":"05.13.018.5174"},["b","4e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/16.7.7-18"},"2 Kgs. 16:7 (7–18)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/20.12"},"2 Ne. 20:12"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-scattering-of"},"TG Israel, Scattering of"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/18.6a","order":"05.13.018.5176"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/neh/3.15"},"Neh. 3:15"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/9.7"},"John 9:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/18.6b","order":"05.13.018.5178"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/7.1.1-6"},"Isa. 7:1 (1–6)"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/18.7a","order":"05.13.018.5180"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.12"},"Isa. 10:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/18.8a","order":"05.13.018.5182"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/30.28"},"Isa. 30:28"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/18.9a","order":"05.13.018.5184"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/joel/3.9.9-14"},"Joel 3:9 (9–14)"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/18.12a","order":"05.13.018.5186"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/31.1.1-3"},"Isa. 31:1 (1–3)"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/18.14a","order":"05.13.018.5188"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/9.33.32-33"},"Rom. 9:33 (32–33)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/cornerstone"},"TG Cornerstone"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-prophecies-about"},"Jesus Christ, Prophecies about"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/18.14b","order":"05.13.018.5190"},["b","14b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/8.14.13-15"},"Isa. 8:14 (13–15)"],";"